DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the pharmacokinetics of NVP-1205 and coadministration of rosuvastatin and ezetimibe.
DOC.brief_title: Compare the Pharmacokinetics of NVP-1205 and Coadministration of Rosuvastatin and Ezetimibe
DOC.criteria: Healthy male subjects age between 19 and 55 signed informed consent subjects have a history of allergy reaction of this drug or other drugs
